ﬁles past and follows the traﬃc into a line that is bound for the next exit. He
follows the ramp as it curves up and around and directs him away from the
traﬃc. After a short spell on this residential looking road, he ﬁnds the turn he
needs.
</p><!--l. 4116--><p class="indent" >  Finally he is oﬀ the freeway and onto the narrow road that leads towards to hills. It
