</p><!--l. 4259--><p class="indent" >  “I see. So you&#x2019;ve been spoiled by our taxpayers before then.” He winks.
</p><!--l. 4261--><p class="indent" >  Another man sees the general and comes over to them. “General,” he acknowledges
