</p><!--l. 11078--><p class="indent" >  “Hello?”
</p><!--l. 11080--><p class="indent" >  “Good morning. Did you sleep well.”
</p><!--l. 11082--><p class="indent" >  “Better. I&#x2019;ll get used to it.”
</p><!--l. 11084--><p class="indent" >  “I have some news about your friends at home. I can tell you when you come in.
We&#x2019;ll be meeting at nine o&#x2019;clock. Join us at the station then. okay?”
</p><!--l. 11088--><p class="indent" >  “Okay. I&#x2019;ll be there.”
</p><!--l. 11090--><p class="indent" >  “Everything okay?”
</p><!--l. 11092--><p class="indent" >  She nods. “I&#x2019;m just out for a walk. I&#x2019;ll check how to get back. Maybe there is a tram
