</p><!--l. 11095--><p class="indent" >  “Where are you?”
</p><!--l. 11097--><p class="indent" >  “I&#x2019;m not sure.”
</p><!--l. 11099--><p class="indent" >  Bishop laughs. “You&#x2019;ll be ﬁne. See you in a while.”
