</p><!--l. 11105--><p class="indent" >  At the Los Angeles airport terminal, ﬂocks of passengers emerge from their
check-in lines in a cross-stream. People pour out of one queue and collide with those
from another with notable disregard for one another&#x2019;s predicament. They meet like
