dishes for cups. He watches her thin body move in a pair of light blue jeans and
narrow black polo-neck. The clothes look old, but they reveal her small breast and

buttocks and her long thin legs. He cannot help from looking at her. She is
perfect.
</p><!--l. 16131--><p class="indent" >  “I said I would,” he manages.
</p><!--l. 16133--><p class="indent" >  “I don&#x2019;t get many visitors,” she says. “Shall I make tea? I think I have some. It&#x2019;s
probably still all right.”
</p><!--l. 16136--><p class="indent" >  He nods. “Yes, please. Tea&#x2019;s ﬁne.”
</p><!--l. 16138--><p class="indent" >  She nods without emotion, acknowledging that now she has to wash two cups from
the pile of plates and crockery in her kitchen sink. She rattles around for a while and
he hears a kettle start to roar.
</p><!--l. 16142--><p class="indent" >  He starts to look around as she works. The TV is showing some kind of junk show.
He doesn&#x2019;t bother to look at it. The remote control is placed strategically on the arm of
