thing going on.
</p><!--l. 16170--><p class="indent" >  “I used to hang out in that crowd before I moved here.”
</p><!--l. 16172--><p class="indent" >  “On crosses?” he says, “Like Jesus?”
</p><!--l. 16174--><p class="indent" >  She laughs, or almost. There was at least a smile there for a moment that seemed
