<!--l. 16222--><p class="nopar" > No kidding, Dermot thinks.
</p><!--l. 16225--><p class="indent" >  “Probably some kind of memory error,” he says.
</p><!--l. 16227--><p class="indent" >  She looks at him expectantly.
</p><!--l. 16229--><p class="indent" >  “I only use it for VR. I like the chat rooms. I like ﬂirting with men, making them
