<!--l. 16543--><p class="indent" >  The car deposits them at the rotating door of the Research council. Some light snow
has fallen and the steps are slippery. Jonas carries Martin under his arm, up the steps
and through the rotating portal.
</p><!--l. 16547--><p class="indent" >  “Mr. Lindgren, they are waiting for you in meeting room four.”
</p><!--l. 16549--><p class="indent" >  Fabulous.
</p><!--l. 16551--><p class="indent" >  “All right, I&#x2019;ll be there as soon as I can.”
</p><!--l. 16553--><p class="indent" >  He sets Martin down and pulls him gently to the elevator. He needs to
install Martin in his oﬃce before he can join any meetings, or catch up on his
messages.
</p><!--l. 16557--><p class="indent" >  He sees on his wristband that Joe has called back and apologized for not being able
