Turks.”
</p><!--l. 23102--><p class="indent" >  Preeta looks around questioningly. “Turks?”
</p><!--l. 23105--><p class="indent" >  “There&#x2019;s a lot of Turkish and Algerian immigrants who work in the cleaning
