<span 
class="ptmri7t-x-x-109">seen. He wants her.</span>
</p><!--l. 28115--><p class="indent" >  <span 
class="ptmri7t-x-x-109">They hit it oﬀ and end up back at his place.</span>
</p><!--l. 28117--><p class="indent" >  <span 
